        <p>With a population of approximately 8.2 Lakh, Salem presents unique pest management challenges. Dense urban living, humid climate, and rapid construction activity create ideal conditions for cockroaches, termites, mosquitoes, rodents, and other pests to thrive.</p>

        <h3>Areas We Serve in Salem</h3>
        <p>Our technicians serve all residential societies, commercial complexes, and industrial areas across Salem and surrounding areas. Same-day service is available for most locations in the city.</p>

        <h3>What Makes Our Service Different in Salem?</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Local experts with deep knowledge of Salem's pest characteristics</li>
          <li>Treatments customised for Salem's specific climate and building types</li>
          <li>Fast response – most bookings confirmed within 30 minutes</li>
          <li>All services come with a 3-month guarantee</li>
          <li>Transparent pricing – no hidden charges</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="why-choose-box">
