            <li><span>👥</span> Population: ~8.2 Lakh</li>
            <li><span>⚡</span> Same-Day Service Available</li>
            <li><span>🛡️</span> 3-Month Guarantee</li>
            <li><span>💰</span> Best Price In Salem</li>
            <li><span>📞</span> 24/7 Emergency Support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
